title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Express your artistry today while the stars are stoking your receptivity and creativity. Yours or someone elses critical estimation of your talents isnt important. Draw, paint, color, dance, or sing to your hearts delight. Claim quiet time to attain inner communion and receive intuitive insights. Try an old reliable activity like meditating, reading tarot cards, or writing poetry. Fueling your imagination and intuition lifts your spirits, empowering you to touch peoples hearts. Dr. Albert Schweitzer wrote, Example is not the main thing in influencing others. It is the only thing. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
